    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for functional transportation at a lower price point. While the engine and transmission are operational, the car shows significant signs of age and use, including noticeable scratches and some minor dents on the exterior. Inside, the upholstery shows wear and the carpet has some staining. It has been regularly serviced, but the buyer should expect some upcoming maintenance needs, such as a suspension refresh and new tires soon. It\u2019s a reliable runner, but it is certainly not a showpiece.",
