      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in absolute showroom condition. The exterior features its original, factory-fresh paint with a deep, mirror-like luster and zero rock chips, scratches, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats show no signs of wear or creasing, and every switchgear component retains its original tactile feel. Mechanically, the car is flawless, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a complete, chronological service history included. Always garage-kept under a climate-controlled environment and never driven in inclement weather, the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. It drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor. Sale includes all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a folder of maintenance receipts. For the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection.",
